nosSystemActualPowerConsumptionValue.name: nosSystemActualPowerConsumptionValue
nosSystemActualPowerConsumptionValue.description: An INTEGER type object shows power consumption. When this feature is not supported, 0 is set.

nosSystemActualPowerConsumptionUnit.name: nosSystemActualPowerConsumptionUnit
nosSystemActualPowerConsumptionUnit.description: A DisplayString type object, shows unit of power consumption 'W'.

nosSystemActualPowerMinPollingInterval.name: nosSystemActualPowerMinPollingInterval
nosSystemActualPowerMinPollingInterval.description: An INTEGER type object shows minimum time of interval to get above object. Unit of value is a second. This value also shows interval of update. (It's meaningless to get value less than this value, because value won't be updated.) When this feature is not supported, maximum value of INTEGER type is set.

nosSystemExhaustAirFlowValue.name: nosSystemExhaustAirFlowValue
nosSystemExhaustAirFlowValue.description: An INTEGER type object shows air flow. When this feature is not supported, 0 is set.

nosSystemExhaustAirFlowUnit.name: nosSystemExhaustAirFlowUnit
nosSystemExhaustAirFlowUnit.description: A DisplayString type object, shows unit of air flow 'CMH', cubic meter per hour.

nosSystemExhaustAirFlowMinPollingInterva.name: nosSystemExhaustAirFlowMinPollingInterval
nosSystemExhaustAirFlowMinPollingInterva.description: An INTEGER type object shows minimum time of interval to get above object. Unit of value is a second. This value also shows interval of update. (It's meaningless to get value less than this value, because value won't be updated.) When this feature is not supported, maximum value of INTEGER type is set.

nosSystemAmbientTemperatureValue.name: nosSystemAmbientTemperatureValue
nosSystemAmbientTemperatureValue.description: A DisplayString type object shows air flow. When this feature is not supported, 0 is set.

nosSystemAmbientTemperatureUnit.name: nosSystemAmbientTemperatureUnit
nosSystemAmbientTemperatureUnit.description: A DisplayString type object, shows unit of temerature 'degC'.

nosSystemAmbientTemperatureMinPollingInt.name: nosSystemAmbientTemperatureMinPollingInterval
nosSystemAmbientTemperatureMinPollingInt.description: An INTEGER type object shows minimum time of interval to get above object. Unit of value is a second. This value also shows interval of update. (It's meaningless to get value less than this value, because value won't be updated.) When this feature is not supported, maximum value of INTEGER type is set.

nosSystemPowerSourceType.name: nosSystemPowerSourceType
nosSystemPowerSourceType.description: A DisplayString type object, shows type of input power, such as 'AC' or 'DC'. When this feature is not supported, (NULL) will be set.

nosSystemPowerSourcePhase.name: nosSystemPowerSourcePhase
nosSystemPowerSourcePhase.description: An Integer type object, shows type of phase of input power, such as 2, single phase, or 3, 3 phase. When this feature is not supported, 0 will be set.

nosSystemPowerSourceVoltage.name: nosSystemPowerSourceVoltage
nosSystemPowerSourceVoltage.description: An Integer type object, shows input voltage, such as 100 or 200. When this feature is not supported, 0 will be set.

nosSystemPermittedPowerConsumptionValue.name: nosSystemPermittedPowerConsumptionValue
nosSystemPermittedPowerConsumptionValue.description: An INTEGER type object shows maximum power consumption which will consume maximum power over variety of configurations. When this feature is not supported, 0 is set.

nosSystemPermittedPowerConsumptionUnit.name: nosSystemPermittedPowerConsumptionUnit
nosSystemPermittedPowerConsumptionUnit.description: A DisplayString type object, shows unit of power consumption 'W'.
